casebody.data:
Henry Hess, as Assignee etc., Respondent v. Nathaniel Hess, Jr., et al., Appellants. Decided March 14, 1889. Appeal by defendants from judgment entered upon verdict for plaintiff. Otto Horwitz, for appellants. W. J. Townsend, for respondent.

Before Sedgwick, Ch. J., and Ingraham, J.

Per Curiam.

Judgment affirmed with costs.
